CustomField.description: This field will be used for Expere Doc Prep, which has not yet been implemented. This field is not required. If enabled, an initial rate (i.e. a teaser rate) was applied to the account. If disabled, this field is not used. By default, it is disabled.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If true an initial rate (i.e. a teaser rate) was applied to the account.
CustomField.label: Initial Rate Indicator
